Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
22 Sep 2022	navhl20	ChangeRequest 53900: EUP - VBS MTN - [4] - Search Screen
14 Jul 2023	navma1	ChangeRequest 59136: EUP | VBS Edi Enhancement [1]
22 Nov 2023 navlc30 ChangeRequest 61256: EUP | FR | 54329 | VBS - Pending issues - Issue 12
